702696f.title: Brooklyn: 29th Street - Kings Highway
702696f.text:
East 29th Street, cars thereon; north from Kings Highway.
October 6, 1933.
Irvin Fitterman.

705228f-a.title: Brooklyn: Kings Highway - 29th Street (East)
705228f-a.text:
Kings Highway, east from East 29th Street.
October 6, 1933.
Irvin Fitterman.
